Nay,butthisdotageofourgeneral's
O'erflowsthemeasure:thosehisgoodlyeyes,
Thato'erthefilesandmustersofthewar
Haveglow'dlikeplatedMars,nowbend,nowturn,
Theofficeanddevotionoftheirview
Uponatawnyfront:hiscaptain'sheart,
Whichinthescufflesofgreatfightshathburst
Thebucklesonhisbreast,renegesalltemper,
Andisbecomethebellowsandthefan
Tocoolagipsy'slust.
