CaesarandAntonyshallwellgreettogether:
Hiswifethat'sdeaddidtrespassestoCaesar;
Hisbrotherwarr'duponhim;although,Ithink,
NotmovedbyAntony.
Iknownot,Menas,
Howlesserenmitiesmaygivewaytogreater.
Were'tnotthatwestandupagainstthemall,
'Twerepregnanttheyshouldsquarebetween
themselves;
Fortheyhaveentertainedcauseenough
Todrawtheirswords:buthowthefearofus
Maycementtheirdivisionsandbindup
Thepettydifference,weyetnotknow.
Be'tasourgodswillhave't!Itonlystands
Ourlivesupontouseourstrongesthands.
