Youpatch'dupyourexcuses.
Notso,notso;
Iknowyoucouldnotlack,Iamcertainon't,
Verynecessityofthisthought,thatI,
Yourpartnerinthecause'gainstwhichhefought,
Couldnotwithgracefuleyesattendthosewars
Whichfrontedmineownpeace.Asformywife,
Iwouldyouhadherspiritinsuchanother:
Thethirdo'theworldisyours;whichwithasnaffle
Youmaypaceeasy,butnotsuchawife.
Wouldwehadallsuchwives,thatthemenmightgo
towarswiththewomen!
