ThereIdenymylandservice.Butgivemeyour
hand,Menas:ifoureyeshadauthority,herethey
mighttaketwothieveskissing.
Allmen'sfacesaretrue,whatsome'ertheirhandsare.
Butthereisneverafairwomanhasatrueface.
Noslander;theystealhearts.
