Thewaywhichpromisesassurance;and
Giveupyourselfmerelytochanceandhazard,
Fromfirmsecurity.
I'llfightatsea.
Ihavesixtysails,Caesarnonebetter.
Ouroverplusofshippingwillweburn;
And,withtherestfull-mann'd,fromtheheadofActium
BeattheapproachingCaesar.Butifwefail,
Wethencando'tatland.
Thybusiness?
Thenewsistrue,mylord;heisdescried;
