Heisdead,Caesar:
Notbyapublicministerofjustice,
Norbyahiredknife;butthatselfhand,
Whichwrithishonourintheactsitdid,
Hath,withthecouragewhichtheheartdidlendit,
Splittedtheheart.Thisishissword;
Irobb'dhiswoundofit;beholditstain'd
